                label.form-label(for="repair_and_maintenance") दुरुस्ती व देखभाल
                input.form-control(type="number" step="any" id="repair_and_maintenance" name="repair_and_maintenance" value=prapatraECurrent.repair_and_maintenance placeholder=" ")

